xnoise (0.1.24.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * GUI changes (mainly new track progess bar, remove old stuff from
    settings dialog, repeat button layout)
  * introduce extendable itemhandler architecture
  * use lazy-loading in media browser to make handling of
    large collections easy and application start ultra fast
  * asynchronous import for lastused items into tracklist on
    application start
  * introduce io worker for slow io tasks (to improve long running
    media import performance)
  * show video thumbnails, if available
  * changed db structure (old databases are not migrated!)
  * update translations
  * bug fixes

 -- Jörn Magens <shuerhaaken@googlemail.com>  Fri, 20 May 2011 15:55:50 +0200
